Final Interview Tips
  • Focus first on Kubernetes, Terraform, GitHub Actions, Helm, and Argo CD.
  • Practice kubectl, helm, terraform, and GitHub Actions YAML daily.
  • Be ready to explain real production incidents.
  • Learn troubleshooting flow more than definitions.
  • Prepare architecture explanation from your real projects.
  • Practice whiteboard scenarios and root cause analysis.
  • Revise CI/CD pipeline end-to-end.
  • Practice Linux troubleshooting commands.
  • Understand monitoring and observability concepts.
  • Be confident while explaining production issues.
